  "title": "chore: Fix #6692 update hogan.js to remove deprecated package mkdirp",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nHello, \r\nCurrent instantsearch.js embed hogan.js as dependency which used mkdirp, which triggers a deprecated warning.\r\nIt's a small change but my team and I would like to avoid install deprecated packages in production. \r\n\r\nTherefore I have forked hogan.js to use native nodejs and remove the mkdirp packages. \r\nAll tests are running correctly for hogan.js.\r\n\r\nLet me know if that can be of any help",
